# 📅 React Booking App

A modern, responsive booking management application built with React and Firebase.  
Designed as a reusable scheduling solution for service-based businesses such as trainers, salons, consultants, and creators.

---

## 🚀 Live Demo
👉 [View Live App](https://servicesbookingapp.netlify.app/)

---

## ✨ Features

- Service selection and booking flow
- Date and time slot scheduling
- Real-time booking storage (Firebase)
- Admin dashboard with authentication
- Booking status management (confirm / cancel / restore)
- Upcoming / past booking filters
- Responsive mobile-first design
- Clean, minimalist UI

---

## 🧱 Tech Stack

**Frontend**
- React (Vite)
- CSS
- clsx (conditional styling)

**Backend / Database**
- Firebase Firestore
- Firebase Auth

**Deployment**
- Netlify

---

## 🖥️ Screens

- Booking flow
- Confirmation
- Admin dashboard
- Mobile responsive layout

---

## 🔐 Admin Access

The dashboard is protected by Firebase Authentication.

Admins can:

- View all bookings
- Cancel or restore bookings
- Track upcoming vs past appointments

